dynamicalSystems
Class Flow

java.lang.Object
  dynamicalSystems.Entity
      dynamicalSystems.Element
          dynamicalSystems.Flow

public class Flow
extends Element

A Flow is an Element that is interrelated with the Stocks, meaning that something is being subtracted/added from/to Stock.

A flow may also be interrelated with converters or even with other flows.

Author:
Wellington Bruno
